Cc cu hi thng gp

Vay tn chp l g? Li sut, thi hn v cch tr n khi vay tn chp ti VPBank l bao nhiu?

Tr li:
Vay tn chp l hnh thc cho vay khng cn ti sn m bo (TSB), da hon ton vo uy tn ca khch hng (KH) v nng lc tr n, phc v cho nhu cu tiu dng c nhn.

Li sut vay ti thiu t 1,2%/thang tng ng 14.4%/nm v ti a 59%/nm ty tng khon vay v theo thi gian d n gim dn. Bn vui lng lin h vi nhn vin ca VPBank c t vn mc li sut c th.

Hng thng VPBank s gi tin nhn thng bo s tin gc, li v ngy thanh ton n s in thoi ng k ca KH. KH vui lng n Chi nhnh VPBank gn nht thanh ton s tin c thng bo hoc chuyn khon vo ti khon ca KH m ti VPBank.

Th tc vay online bao gm g ?

Tr li:
KH cn cung cp h s theo quy nh ca VPBank, bao gm:
+ H s chng minh nhn thn (CMND/H chiu/Cn cc cng dn)
+ H s chng minh ni c tr (H khu/Bng li xe)
+ H s chng minh cng vic (HL/Quyt nh bin ch/Xc nhn nhn s)
+ H s chng minh thu nhp (Sao k lng/Xc nhn lng/bng lng)

Nhn vin VPBank s t vn c th cho KH.

ng k trn vayonline mang li li ch g ?

Tr li:
Bn khng cn phi ti ngn hng, v ch khi h s c ph duyt bn mi cn k h s. Yu cu vay vn ca bn c tip nhn v phn hi ngay trong ngy. Thi gian x l h s nhanh hn nhiu so vi vic bn t ti ngn hng vay.

Cc loi ph c th pht sinh khi vay tn chp ti VPBank?

Tr li:
Ph bo him khon vay:
+ Mc ch: bo him cho khon vay tn chp ti VPBank, trong trng hp xy ra ri ro KH khng c kh nng tr n (t vong hoc thng tt ton b vnh vin), cng ty bo him s ng ra chi tr ton b d n cn li ca KH cho VPBank.
+ Mc ph: 1,3 1,8%/nm tnh trn d n gim dn, VPBank s tnh tng s tin bo him ca KH trong sut thi hn vay v thu ton b s tin ny ti thi im gii ngn.

Ph pht tr n trc hn
+ Ni dung: KH tt ton trc hn s chu ph pht tr n trc hn.
+ Mc ph:
*Nu thi gian vay thc t n 12 thng: Ph tr n trc hn c tnh bng 4% nhn (x) s tin tr n trc hn, ti thiu l 1.000.000 ng.
*Nu thi gian vay thc t trn 12 thng: Ph tr n trc hn c tnh bng 3 % nhn (x) s tin tr n trc hn, ti thiu l 600.000 ng.

Ph tr n trc hn c p dng trong trng hp Khch hng tr n trc hn ton b hoc mt phn d n khon vay ca Khch hng.
Mt nm c hiu l 365 ngy.

Nu ti thanh ton n chm tr, hoc khng thanh ton th s nh th no?

Tr li:
Nu bn thanh ton n chm tr hoc khng thanh ton, khon vay ca bn s b chuyn thnh n qu hn, nh hng n uy tn, lch s tn dng ca KH. Ngoi ra, i vi phn gc v li qu hn, bn s phi chu li sut bng 150% mc li sut trong hn:
+ Li sut cho vay p dng i vi d n gc qu hn (li sut qu hn): Bng 150% mc li sut cho vay trong hn p dng ti thi im chuyn n qu hn.
+ Li sut chm tr p dng i vi tin li chm tr: Bng 150% li sut cho vay trong hn p dng ti thi im chm tr li nhng ti a khng qu 10%/nm tnh trn s d li chm tr tng ng vi thi gian chm tr.
